aw%20Bill%26quot%3B%20Demand%20To%20PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20has%20written%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20seeking%20his%20personal%20intervention%20to%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%20which%20was%20introduced%20in%20parliament%20today%20for%20debate%20and%20passing.%20All%20the%20non-NDA%20parties%2C%20including%20Mr%20Stalin's%20DMK%2C%20have%20united%20to%20block%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Assembly%20has%20already%20passed%20a%20resolution%20to%20urge%20the%20Centre%20to%20withdraw%20the%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20letter%2C%20Mr%20Stalin%20said%20the%20Constitution%20grants%20every%20citizen%20the%20right%20to%20follow%20their%20respective%20religion%20and%20it%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20elected%20governments%20to%20uphold%20and%20protect%20this%20right.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20proposed%20amendments%20in%20the%20bill%20have%20not%20taken%20that%20into%20consideration%20and%20the%20amended%20law%20is%20%26quot%3Bbound%20to%20severely%20harm%20the%20interest%20of%20Muslim%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20cited%20multiple%20points%20in%20his%20letter%20to%20cite%20how%20the%20bill%20can%20interfere%20with%20and%20undermine%20the%20religious%20autonomy%20of%20the%20Waqf%20boards%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Muslim%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20examples%2C%20he%20cited%20the%20proposed%20mandatory%20inclusion%20of%20two%20non-Muslim%20members%20in%20waqf%20boards.%20The%20removal%20of%20the%20'Waqf%20by%20user'%20provision%20threatens%20the%20status%20of%20many%20historical%20Waqf%20properties%2C%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stipulation%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bindividuals%20who%20practiced%20Islam%20for%20at%20least%20five%20years%20only%20can%20donate%20properties%20to%20Waqf%20will%20prevent%20non-Muslims%20from%20donating%20properties%20to%20Waqf%20which%20wi