d%20by%20the%20Congress'%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%2C%20who%20first%20accused%20Mr%20Rijiju%20of%20making%20%26quot%3Bmisleading%20statements%26quot%3B%20and%20labelled%20the%20Waqf%20amendments%20%26quot%3Ban%20assault%20on%20the%20Constitution%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gogoi%20also%20asked%20why%20the%20Minority%20Affairs%20Ministry%20did%20not%20mention%20this%20bill%20in%20any%20of%20the%20four%20meetings%20of%20its%20parliamentary%20committee%20in%202023%2C%20a%20year%20before%20the%20amendments%20were%20presented.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EKiren%20Rijiju%20Sets%20Ball%20Rolling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20case%20going%20on%20since%201970%20in%20Delhi%20involved%20several%20properties%2C%20including%20the%20Parliament%20building.%20The%20Delhi%20Waqf%20Board%20had%20claimed%20these...%20the%20case%20was%20in%20court%20but%20then%20the%20UPA%20denotified%20123%20properties%20and%20gave%20them%20to%20the%20Waqf%20Board%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said%20on%20the%20'Parliament%20to%20Waqf'%20charge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20After%20introducing%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20says%20%26quot%3BIn%202013%2C%20right%20before%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%202014%2C%20there%20were%20some%20steps%20taken%20which%20will%20raise%20questions%20in%20your%20mind.%20In%202013%2C%20the%20act%20was%20changed%20to%20allow%20Sikhs%2C%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F6LSe1Wg53D%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F6LSe1Wg53D%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1907334514780553614%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%202%2C%202025%