te.%20It%20is%20simply%20a%20matter%20of%20property%20management.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FChEqLgUz8g%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FChEqLgUz8g%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1907339369452564688%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%202%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rijiju%20also%20pointed%20out%20the%20government%20had%20removed%20a%20%26quot%3Bdraconian%20provision%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20existing%20Waqf%20laws%20-%20a%20provision%2C%20he%20said%2C%20that%20allowed%20%26quot%3Bany%20land%20to%20be%20declared%20as%20Waqf%20property%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20previously%20any%20land%20could%20be%20declared%20as%20Waqf%20property.%20But%20we%20have%20removed%20that%20provision.%20This%20provision%20was%20misused%20to%20such%20an%20extent%20the%20number%20of%20properties%20increased%20to%20lakhs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20emphasise%20his%20point%2C%20Mr%20Rijiju%20said%20temples%20and%20gurdwaras%20had%20been%20claimed%20as%20Waqf%20land%20despite%20no%20records%20of%20mosques%20in%20those%20areas.%20%26quot%3BSurendereshwar%20Temple%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20was%20declared%20Waqf...%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20thousands%20of%20acres%20of%20land...%20in%20Haryana%2C%20a%20Sikh%20gurudwara%20was%20also%20declared%20Waqf...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWaqf%20boards%20control%20the%20third%20largest%20pool%20of%20properties%20in%20the%20country%2C%20after%20the%20Railways%20and%20Defence%2C%20but%20those%20belong%20to%20the%20nation.%20Waqf%20properties%20are%20private...%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20stressing%20also%20the%20proposed%20changes%20to%20the%20law%20would%20not%20be%20retrospective%2C%20as%20some%20opposition%20MPs%20had%20warned%20they%20would%20be.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20opposition%20should%2C%20therefore%2C%20not%20spread%20misinformation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued%2C%20slamming%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20parties%20for%20trying%20to%20politicise%20the%20issue.%20%26quot%3BAppeasement%20does%20not%20lead%20to%20votes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20charge%20is%20significant%2C%20given%20that%20changes%20to%20the%20Waqf%20laws%20comes%20as%20Bihar%20-%20where%20the%20Muslim%20population%20is%20around%2017%20per%20cent%20-%20votes%20in%20an%20Assembly%20election%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20come%20with%20a%20very%20clear%20brief...%20we%20want%20the%20Waqf%20to%20be%20secular%2C%20inclusive%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rijiju%20said%2C%20outlining%20several%20of%20the%20proposed%20changes%2C%20including%20a%20contentious%20rule%20requiring%20two-non%20Muslims%20to%20be%20part%20of%20each%20state%20Waqf%20Board%20and%20the%20central%20Waqf%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Minority%20Affairs%20Minister%20also%20questioned%20the%20lack%20of%20female%20representation%20on%20these%20boards%2C%20declaring%20the%20government%20had%20written%20in%20provisions%20to%20guarantee%20at%20least%20two%20women%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGogoi%2C%20Opposition's%20Rebuttal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20rebuttal%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Gogoi%20referred%20to%20a%20new%20provision%20that%20says%20donations%20to%20Waqf%20boards%20can%20only%20be%20made%20by%20Muslims%20who%20have%20been%20practicing%20for%20at%20least%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProblematic%20clauses%20are%20in%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill...%20it%20is%20sad%20that%20the%20government%20is%20now%20giving%20'religious%20certificates'.%20Will%20they%20seek%20statements%20from%20other%20religions%20also%3F%20What%20kind%20of%20justice%20is%20this%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-lok-sabha-debate-gaurav-gogoi-dilute-defame-divide-disenfranchise-c