0in%201970%20near%20the%20Belarusian%20border.%20It%20had%20everything%20one%20might%20need%2C%20from%20a%20grocery%20store%20to%20a%20restaurant.%20It%20was%20a%20relatively%20new%20city%20with%20a%20vibrant%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20April%2026%2C%201986%2C%20disaster%20struck%20at%20Chernobyl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20plant's%20reactors%20exploded%2C%20sending%20highly%20radioactive%20contamination%20into%20the%20air%20across%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20and%20into%20Europe.%20Pripyat%20was%20evacuated%20the%20day%20after%20the%20deadly%20meltdown%20that%20killed%2030%20operators%20and%20first%20responders.%20It's%20now%20a%20ghost%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20recently%20traveled%20to%20Pripyat%20deep%20inside%20the%20now-established%20Chernobyl%20Exclusion%20Zone%2C%20a%20highly%20radioactive%20area%20of%201%2C000%20square%20miles%20that%20encompasses%20the%20nuclear%20power%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20to%20Pripyat%20was%20no%20easy%20task.%20Visitors%20need%20a%20permit%20to%20enter%20the%20exclusion%20zone%2C%20which%20is%20about%20a%20two-hour%20drive%20north%20of%20Kyiv%2C%20the%20Ukrainian%20capital.%20We%20met%20our%20guide%20at%20the%20entrance%2C%20which%20is%20a%20military%20checkpoint.%20The%20soldiers%20looked%20over%20our%20documents%20before%20allowing%20us%20into%20the%20restricted%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20building%20sits%20behind%20the%20forest%20in%20the%20abandoned%20city%20of%20Pripyat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ec526469253ccddf9af393%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20building%20sits%20behind%20the%20forest%20in%20the%20abandoned%20city%20of%20Pripyat.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDriving%20to%20Pripyat%20through%20the%20actual%20town%20of%20Chernobyl%20and%20past%20the%20nuclear%20power%20plant%20is%