%20adopted%20Lyrik%20when%20she%20was%203.%20I%20also%20realized%20that%20I%20wasn't%20interested%20in%20being%20a%20chiropractor.%20I%20was%20much%20more%20drawn%20to%20the%20marketing%20side%20of%20business.%20So%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20opened%20a%20chiropractic%20clinic%3A%20I%20did%20the%20marketing%20while%20he%20saw%20patients.%20We%20were%20profitable%20within%20three%20months.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjulia-childs-inspired-me-to-cook-when-on-food-stamps-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20was%20on%20welfare%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20I%20added%20up%20all%20the%20benefits%20I'd%20received.%20It%20was%20about%20%2420%2C000.%20I%20vowed%20to%20pay%20them%20back%20one%20day.%20During%20the%20second%20year%20of%20operating%20our%20clinic%2C%20our%20tax%20bill%20was%20almost%20exactly%20that%20amount.%20I%20felt%20like%20I'd%20cleared%20my%20debt%20to%20the%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20started%20placing%20recent%20graduates%20in%20new%20clinics%20and%20then%20selling%20those%20clinics%20to%20those%20doctors.%20It%20was%20lucrative%2C%20and%20today%20my%20net%20worth%20is%20in%20the%20seven%20figures.%20Still%2C%20it%20feels%20strange%20to%20call%20myself%20a%20millionaire.%20I%20have%20more%20security%20than%20I%20used%20to%20and%20don't%20need%20to%20struggle%20to%20survive.%20But%20I%20don't%20feel%20like%20I've%20made%20it%20yet%20or%20like%20I%20can%20coast.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2233357b37-9030-4411-a514-c2af5dcf6b21%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHaving%20Lyrik%20young%20shaped%20my%20success%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELyrik%20has%20always%20been%20at%20my%20side%20as%20I%20built%20my%20businesses.%20When%20she%20was%20little%2C%20we%20used%20to%20drive%20around%20listening%20to%20CDs%20about%20business%20and%20goal%20setting.%20I%20think%20she%20absorbed%20that%20because%20she's%20always%20been