udio%20Ghibli's%20animators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rosenberg%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20outcome%20of%20any%20potential%20lawsuit%20remains%20uncertain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20OpenAI%20were%20marketing%20its%20platform%20as%20a%20place%20where%20consumers%20could%20transform%20their%20photos%20into%20'Ghibli-style'%20anime%2C%20that%20fact%20would%20weigh%20more%20strongly%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20court%20finding%20that%20OpenAI's%20conduct%20violated%20the%20Lanham%20Act%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20courts%20reject%20OpenAI's%20fair%20use%20argument%2C%20Mr%20Rosenberg%20speculated%20that%20AI%20developers%20may%20have%20to%20compensate%20copyright%20holders%20and%20credit%20them%20for%20influencing%20AI-generated%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20clear%20legal%20precedent%20exists%20on%20whether%20OpenAI%20has%20violated%20US%20copyright%20law.%20The%20company%20argues%20that%20training%20its%20models%20falls%20under%20%26quot%3Bfair%20use%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20key%20point%20in%20AI%20copyright%20debates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20copyright%20concerns%2C%20the%20controversy%20could%20also%20impact%20Studio%20Ghibli's%20ability%20to%20monetise%20its%20signature%20art%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Studio%20Ghibli%20ever%20wanted%20to%20launch%20its%20own%20tool%20allowing%20fans%20to%20transform%20photos%20into%20its%20signature%20style%2C%20OpenAI's%20update%20has%20essentially%20taken%20that%20business%20opportunity%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rosenberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20more%20concerning%2C%20he%20added%2C%20was%20the%20possibility%20that%20AI%20could%20generate%20entire%20animations%20in%20the%20Ghibli%20style%2C%20misleading%20audiences%20into%20believing%20they%20were%20official%20works.%20It%20blurs%20%26quot%3Bthe%20line%20between%20homage%20and%20outright%20misrepresentation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743585120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F