E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20both%20sides%20said%20they%20would%20resume%20direct%20flights%20after%20they%20reached%20an%20agreement%20in%20October%20regarding%20patrolling%20their%20Himalayan%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20Tariff%20Threats%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Trump%20is%20set%20to%20unveil%20sweeping%20new%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariffs%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20but%20kept%20the%20world%20guessing%20until%20the%20last%20minute%20about%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20onslaught.%20Trump%20will%20roll%20out%20the%20measures%20flanked%20by%20cabinet%20members%20in%20the%20Rose%20Garden%20of%20the%20White%20House%20at%204%3A00%20pm%20(2000%20GMT)%20--%20after%20Wall%20Street%20markets%20close%20--%20promising%20that%20they%20will%20stop%20America%20from%20being%20%26quot%3Bripped%20off%26quot%3B%20and%20will%20deliver%20a%20new%20%26quot%3Bgolden%20age%26quot%3B%20of%20US%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20nations%20working%20to%20lower%20tariffs%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20appease%20Trump%2C%20who%20has%20called%20New%20Delhi%20a%20%26quot%3Btariff%20king%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Btariff%20abuser%26quot%3B%20and%20has%20vowed%20to%20reciprocate.%20Both%20countries%20have%20started%20talks%20towards%20clinching%20an%20early%20trade%20deal%20and%20resolving%20their%20standoff%20on%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743584640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F3qhfkj48_india-china-trade-reuters_625x300_02_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-ready-to-buy-more-indian-goods-says-beijings-envoy-as-us-tariffs-loom-8068521%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariffs%20threaten%20to%20upend%20the%20global%20trade%20system%2C%20China%20has%20offered%20to%20import%20more%20Indian%20products%20and%20strengthen%20trade%20coop