o%20head%20inland%20instead%20of%20towards%20the%20sea.%20This%20dehydrates%20the%20baby%20turtles%2C%20causing%20them%20to%20die.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20number%20of%20lights%20has%20increased%20dramatically%2C%E2%80%9D%20Arun%20points%20out.%20%E2%80%9CRight%20now%2C%20we%20are%20enjoying%20the%20beach%20as%20a%20place%20of%20recreation%20for%20us.%20But%20making%20the%20beaches%20safe%20for%20them%20to%20nest%20is%20crucial%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Arun.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnsustainable%20fishing%20practices%20remain%20a%20significant%20danger%2C%20as%20turtles%20often%20get%20trapped%20in%20nets%20and%20drown.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20biggest%20threat%20for%20sea%20turtles%20is%20the%20unsustainable%20fishing%20practices%20of%20the%20world%2C%20not%20just%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-03-29T200557.755-1743258963.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20olive%20ridley%20turtle%20on%20the%20shore%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-03-29T200557.755-1743258963.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-03-29T200557.755-1743258963-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-03-29T200557.755-1743258963-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-03-29T200557.755-1743258963-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-03-29T200557.755-1743258963-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-417029%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3