have%20released%20several%20lakh%20baby%20turtles%20into%20the%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESSTCN%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20turned%20Chennai%20into%20a%20key%20nesting%20site.%20%E2%80%9COn%20other%20beaches%20where%20turtles%20can%E2%80%99t%20nest%2C%20they%20have%20moved%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Arun%20explains.%20Their%20impact%20extends%20beyond%20Chennai%2C%20inspiring%20turtle%20conservation%20across%20India.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20the%2090s%20and%202000s%2C%20other%20NGOs%20for%20sea%20turtles%20started%20forming%20along%20the%20coast%2C%20making%20SSTCN%20a%20model%20for%20others%20to%20follow%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kartik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20citizen-driven%20initiative%2C%20SSTCN%20has%20endured%20despite%20bureaucratic%20challenges.%20%E2%80%9CA%20civil%20society%20group%20working%20on%20an%20endangered%20species%20for%2035%20years%20is%20remarkable%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kartik%20notes.%20Their%20work%20has%20also%20raised%20awareness%20and%20included%20them%20in%20key%20environmental%20development%20programmes%20for%20the%20city.%20%E2%80%9CEveryone%20in%20Chennai%20knows%20about%20Olive%20Ridleys%20and%20turtle%20walks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-03-29T200646.484-1743259120.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Arun%20carefully%20taking%20the%20eggs%20out%20of%20the%20nest%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-03-29T200646.484-1743259120.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-03-29T200646.484-1743259120-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-03-29T200646.484-1743259120-500x262.jpg%205